一、圖書作者與內容簡介：<BR>
     Spencer Johnson was an American author. His stories of timeless and simple truths have changed the work and lives of millions of readers. This time, Johnson brings us the gift which provides practical guidance for these turbulent times. It is an amazing story surrounding a young man looking for the gift making him happy. Through the exploration of the young man, we get to find what the gift in our lives actually is. <br />
<br />

<BR>
二、內容摘錄：<BR>
     You already know what the present is. (p. 19)     <br />
<br />
     The present is not the past and it is not the future. The present is the present moment! The present is right now. (P. 31)<br />
<br />
     It is hard to let go of the past if you have not learned from the past. As soon as you learn and let go, you improve the present today. (P. 50)<br />
<br />
     Being more successful means becoming more of whom you are capable of being. Each of us defines for ourselves what it means to be more successful. (P. 79)<br />
<br />

